x19 h35 y1db9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plainly revealed in the Scriptures, and inseparably interwoven </div><div class="t m345 x19 h35 y10d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with human history... . </div><div class="t m109 x51 h35 y13f5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Before the creation of man, angels were in existence; for </div><div class="t m105 x19 h35 y10d5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">when the foundations of the earth were laid, &apos;the morning stars </div><div class="t m2d5 x19 h35 y12f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sang together, and all the sons of God shouted for joy.&apos; Job. </div><div class="t m915 x19 h35 y10dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">38:7. After the fall of man, angels were sent to guard the tree of </div><div class="t m4a5 x19 h35 y1c9e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life, and this before a human being had died. Angels are in </div><div class="t m146f x19 h35 ya13 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nature superior to men.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m55e x54 h35 y143d ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t mced xcc h35 y143d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 511. </div><div class="t mf6f x51 h5 y2126 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is the origin of evil angels? Rev. 12:9; 2 Peter 2:4. </div><div class="t mb06 x51 h35 y1312 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sin originated among the angels of heaven. Those who re- </div><div class="t mb18 x19 h35 y108c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fused to live in obedience were expelled. </div><div class="t m61b x51 h35 y10f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Evil spirits, in the beginning created sinless, were equal in </div><div class="t m58a x19 h35 y14c9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nature, power, and glory with the holy beings that are now </div><div class="t m1160 x19 h35 y10fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s messengers.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m1f5 x56 h35 y10fe ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m1ea xba h35 y1d94 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 513. </div><div class="t m47c x51 h5 y1107 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How are these evil supernatural powers referred to by Paul? </div><div class="t me89 x19 h5 y1402 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eph. 2:2; 6:12. </div><div class="t m394 x51 h35 y1544 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We do not understand as we should the great conflict going </div><div class="t m1cb x19 h35 y14db ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on between invisible agencies, the controversy between loyal </div><div class="t m374 x19 h35 ye81 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and disloyal angels. Over every man, good and evil angels strive. </div><div class="t mcdb x19 h35 y1463 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is no make-believe conflict.&quot;—Evangelism, p. 704. </div><div class="t m5 x93 h5 y2e8a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m2ca6 x3 h5 y1506 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THINK IT THROUGH </div><div class="t m5 xa h5 y1506 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t ma5e x51 h5 y105e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Actors can portray apt characterizations of other people. </div><div class="t m5d1 x19 h5 y14fa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why would this be easy for evil angels to do? </div><div class="t m5 x93 h5 y2e8a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m16ae x27 h5 y11ea ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY </div><div class="t m5 x6 h5 y11ea ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1126 x51 h35 y11ea ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m626 x70 h35 y11ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 492-499. </div><div class="t m19f3 xb9 h5 y1ebb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">90 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
